      <para id="id6085341">Description of stroke on the drum:</para>
      <para id="id6178117">Pitch</para>
      <para id="id1169575520292">As we all differ physically you must decide for yourself when the stroke sounds and feels good. You must ask yourself <emphasis effect="bold">why </emphasis>a specific stroke sounds better and what did you do to obtain a better sound.</para>
      <figure id="id1169574327708">
