      <para id="id8195034">
        <emphasis effect="bold">Rhythmic patterns</emphasis>
        <emphasis effect="bold">: drum</emphasis>
      </para>
      <para id="id1169575925848">To perform these patterns on the drum requires skill. </para>
      <list id="id1169578800576" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Decide beforehand which techniques you intend using. </item>
